				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Your problem is that your music engine is trying to use the same RAM that Vegaplay is using to store sprites and track numbers and so they're messing with each other's memory. You need to either change the memory locations your music engine uses, or edit vegaplay.asm to use $200 instead of $700 for the start of the sprite buffer.</div>

